author: Lee Moran
title: Bill Maher Dissects Donald Trump's Second Week In Power
text:
Bill Maher Dissects Donald Trump's Second Week In Power "Welcome to this week’s edition of ‘he did what?'" 02/04/2017 02:35 am ET Lee Moran Trends Editor, The Huffington Post Bill Maher didn’t hold back when it came to analyzing President Donald Trump’s second week in office. On Friday’s broadcast of “ Real Time, ” he tore into Trump over the president’s Muslim travel ban , for picking a fight with Australia, for threatening Iran and for trying to make Black History Month all about himself. All in just seven days. “Welcome to this week’s edition of ‘he did what?’” said Maher at the top of the show. “There’s so much news this guy creates.” 
Check out the full segment above. Related Coverage
